Wow. i think im in love. so last night me and my mom went on a cookie baking frenzy. we made some rediculas amount of cookies like 12 different kinds or something. my aunt an uncle came over and braught us gifts from mexico. i got a really pretty bracelet. then at like 9:30 james showed up and was here till 2' baking cookies with me. we had so much fun. it was awesome. for all u people out there who think its not gonna work, it is and i am wicked excited about it. lol its just so fun to prove people wrong. now its 8 in the morning and i have to write a term paper for history. i need to be at the school for 3' this afternoon. that sucks wicked bad. oh well i guess. we get to go sing with that gay ass dude and his sexy blue shirt. ok well im gonna stop procrastinating now and go do homework.
